title: 12/22: Weekend Recap - Daniel Jones for the Win! (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Ok maybe you didn't start Daniel Jones, but you may have started Andy Dalton or Kenyan Drake or Tyler Higbee to win your league. Let's recap! We talk about the big injuries (2:51), our best calls (4:40) and worst calls (6:24) of Week 16, the biggest duds of the week (8:33) and NFL playoff scenarios you need to know if you're playing Week 17 (10:25) ... The Best of Week 16 (12:45)! Ryan Fitzpatrick, Devonta Freeman, Alvin Kamara, Hunter Renfrow and more. Plus winners and losers (29:30) and MegaDuds (33:40) ... Recapping every game with a "Believe it or Not" for 2020 (40:40) ... Email us at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
